title: Durham says CIA found data alleging Trump-Russia connection not 'technically plausible,' was 'user created' - Fox News
content: Durham says CIA found data alleging Trump-Russia connection not 'technically plausible,' was 'user created'  Fox NewsView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Special Counsel John Durham asserted in a court filing Friday that the CIA concluded data from Clinton campaign lawyer Michael Sussmann alleging coordination between Donald Trump and Russia was "not technically plausible" and was "user created."
